OL,4,CThomas Gainsborough's Blue Boy to
OL,5,Creturn to the UK after 100 years
OL,6, One of British art's most famous
OL,7, paintings, The Blue Boy by Thomas
OL,8, Gainsborough, is to return to the UK
OL,9, 100 years after it left.
OL,11,FThe 1770 masterpiece will be loaned to
OL,12,Fthe National Gallery, where it will go
OL,13,Fon display on 25 January 2022.
OL,15,FThe London gallery's 1922 farewell show
OL,16,Ffor the work attracted 90,000 visitors
OL,17,Fafter it was sold to a US businessman.
OL,19,FCurrent National Gallery director Dr
OL,20,FGabriele Finaldi said the work showed
OL,21,FGainsborough at "his dazzling best".
